<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Account Recovery</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        color: #333;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        color: #007bff;
        text-align: center;
      }
      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .link {
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: normal;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .link a {
        color: #0000EE;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .link a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Change Password Request</h1>
      <p>Dear User,</p>
      <p>You have requested a password change. Please click the following link to proceed:</p>
      <div class="link"><a href="{{ link }}" target="_blank">{{ link }}</a></div>
      <p>This link is valid for a limited time only. If you did not initiate this request, please ignore this email and contact customer service for support.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>Bot V2 Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
